result.name: ecosim-outputs-from-mediterranean-model-used-to-look-at-potential-impact-of-non-native-species-
result.notes:
Outputs from Bay of Calvi Ecosim model- used to look at potential impact of 
non-native species. Biomasses of organisms at the start of simulations and 
those after 100 years, assuming different population growth trajectories for 
the alien fish species Fisurella.
